  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b>Will</b> is a common name in Westeros and may refer to:\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Will\" title=\"Will\">Will</a>, a ranger of the Night's Watch</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Will_(orphan)\" title=\"Will (orphan)\">Will (orphan)</a>, a boy taken in by Willow Heddle at the crossroads inn</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Will_(squire)\" title=\"Will (squire)\">Will (squire)</a>, the squire of Ser Uthor Underleaf</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Will_Bean\" title=\"Will Bean\">Will Bean</a>, a farmer in service to House Osgrey of Standfast</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Will_(Treb)\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Will (Treb)\">Will (Treb)</a>, nicknamed \"Treb\", another farmer in service to House Osgrey</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Will_the_Stork\" title=\"Will the Stork\">Will the Stork</a>, a hedge knight</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Will_of_the_Woods\" title=\"Will of the Woods\">Will of the Woods</a>, a sellsword with the Windblown</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Will_Cole\" title=\"Will Cole\">Will Cole</a>, a sellsword serjeant with the Golden Company</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Will_Humble\" title=\"Will Humble\">Will Humble</a>, a member of House Humble on the Iron Islands</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Will_Short\" title=\"Will Short\">Will Short</a>, a man of the North</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Fletcher_Will\" title=\"Fletcher Will\">Fletcher Will</a>, an inhabitant of the Riverlands</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Hookface_Will\" title=\"Hookface Will\">Hookface Will</a>, a guard at Dragonstone</li></ul>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404213833\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.003 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.004 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 1/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 4/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 1/40\nExpensive parser funct